}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathsf {isTruncated}\,
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen n-1\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\,A is a proposition. By our inductive hypothesis, this is a dependent product of propositions (Corollary ).

